00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:46,416
And she might have known Harold Slade.

343
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:48,440
Oh, she doesn't know what she knows.

344
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:50,320
She's unstable as you would be.

