384
00:30:18,160 --> 00:30:19,520
Are you religious?

385
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:27,840
Uh, no, not really.

386
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:30,920
<i>What do you believe in?</i>

387
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:33,920
I don't know.

388
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:36,040
Science, I guess.

389
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:39,680
Logic, patterns.

390
00:30:40,360 --> 00:30:42,040
<i>What about the other stuff?</i>

