00:30:43,320 --> 00:30:44,600
<i>Other stuff?</i>

392
00:30:49,000 --> 00:30:50,480
Ghosts...

393
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:56,920
uh, fate, miracles, luck...

394
00:30:59,320 --> 00:31:00,440
