00:37:43,120 --> 00:37:44,280
Write this down,

452
00:37:45,040 --> 00:37:48,040
<i>Turnpike house,
Paintmoor Lane, North Tamford.</i>

453
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:50,640
<i>I think Harold Slade had a pseudonym</i>

