00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:13,960
Fuck it.

483
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:16,320
Ellen, listen to me.

484
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:19,680
No, you don't need to call the police...

485
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:22,800
